# Local development URLs
http://localhost:4321/.*

# Rate-limited social hosts
https://(www\.)?instagram\.(com|cl)/.*

# Template placeholders in vendored or source code
https://www\.googletagmanager\.com/ns\.html\?id=\$\{gtmContainerId\}

# Preconnect and analytics hosts that are not meaningful navigable pages
https://www\.googletagmanager\.com/
https://static\.cloudflareinsights\.com/

# Upstream docs that may fail intermittently in CI
https://www\.npmjs\.com/package/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free
https://docs\.fontawesome\.com/apis/javascript/get-started
